traverse-sensors (0.01) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Package the Traverse Ten64 board sensor hwmon drivers as a DKMS package
    (pac1934, emc2301, emc17xx, emc181x).
  * dkms.conf: build for the target kernel version (KERNELRELEASE=kernelver)
    and AUTOINSTALL=yes so the modules rebuild automatically on kernel
    upgrades.

